    "body": "## Summary\n- Split `ci_install_dependency.sh` helpers: `install_protoc.sh`, `ci_download_flashinfer_jit_cache.sh` (from earlier commit on this branch)\n- Read FlashInfer python pin from pyproject; `USE_UV` / `IS_BLACKWELL` detection; shared apt list; skip redundant nvshmem/cuDNN reinstalls\n- **This PR** adds clearer section structure, restores prior comments, splits killall vs apt timing, and logs per-step elapsed time + UTC timestamps for CI profiling\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] CI: cuda jobs that run `scripts/ci/cuda/ci_install_dependency.sh`\n\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)",
